A gleaming Italian V-twin motorcycle parked on rain-slicked Singapore streets at golden hour, chrome exhaust pipes catching warm light, deep burgundy metallic tank finish reflecting the urban skyline, steam rising from wet asphalt, photorealistic style with shallow depth of field focusing on the muscular engine block, moody atmospheric lighting with orange and purple sunset tones bleeding through modern high-rise buildings in the background, the motorcycle positioned at a dramatic three-quarter angle suggesting power and longing, droplets of water beading on the leather seat.
